headline: Why The Mosaic Company (MOS) Led the Monday Upsurge?

headline: Mosaic to Sell Its Phosphate Mining Unit in Brazil to Fosfatados
summary: MOS decides to sell its Phosphate Mining Unit in Patos de Minas, Brazil, to Fosfatados to redeploy capital to high-returning areas.
